p>Totals and sub-totals have been rounded separately and so may not equal the sum of their rounded parts.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p>","Canterbury","Mr Julian Brazier","38259","2016-06-02T13:07:02.49Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/521141/answer","Biography information for Sir Julian Brazier","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/521141/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/521141/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2016-05-24","Army: Reserve Forces","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, how many people who joined the army reserve force in each year since 2010 subsequently left that force in each of those years.","false","Biography information for Toby Perkins","Chesterfield","Toby Perkins","38260"
